<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Services on Atlas</title><link>https://www.javiercd.es/en/tags/services/</link><description>Recent content in Services on Atlas</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Sep 2023 10:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.javiercd.es/en/tags/services/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Installing and Configuring a DHCP Server on Linux</title><link>https://www.javiercd.es/en/posts/servicios/dhcp/instalacion_y_configuracion_de_un_servidor_dhcp_en_linux/dhcp_ipv4/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 Sep 2023 10:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.javiercd.es/en/posts/servicios/dhcp/instalacion_y_configuracion_de_un_servidor_dhcp_en_linux/dhcp_ipv4/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="configuring-the-dhcp-server-on-debian">Configuring the DHCP Server on Debian&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>In this article, you will learn how to configure the &lt;code>isc-dhcp-server&lt;/code>. Additionally, we will configure an IP reservation and set it up to operate on two different scopes.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Here is my DHCP server&amp;rsquo;s network configuration:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Router external network&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>auto ens4
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>iface ens4 inet dhcp
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Internal network 1&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>auto ens5
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>iface ens5 inet static
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> address 192.168.10.1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> netmask 255.255.255.0
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Internal network 2&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>auto ens6
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>iface ens6 inet static
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> address 192.168.20.1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> netmask 255.255.255.0
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="installing-the-isc-dhcp-server">Installing the isc-dhcp-server&lt;/h2>
